                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">SPEC.</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">YES - IN SPEC.</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">NO - OUT OF SPEC.</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody valign="top">
                        <row>
                            <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                                <para>1.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                                <para>On</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry rotate="0">
                                <para>Insure there is air pressure to the air solenoid pack.</para>
                                <para>Air suspension dump off.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                                <para>Observe suspension air bags.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                                <para>Air bags should inflate.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                                <para>Air suspension solenoid is working correctly.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry rotate="0">
                                <para>Go to next step.</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="1" rotate="0">
                                <para>2.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="2" rotate="0">
                                <para>On</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colspan="5" spanname="SPAN1" rotate="0">
                                <para>Verify problem is not caused by an air plumbing problem. If it appears that the
                                    air suspension solenoid is not operating, go to
                                    <hotlnk document="s082503_X0825922.xml" xrefid="x0825922">Fault Detection
                                        Management.
                                    </hotlnk>
                                    <xref refid="x0825922"/>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
